text: The 1966 Asian Games, officially known as the V Asian Games, was a sports event in Bangkok, Thailand. It occurred from December 9 to December 20, 1966. There were 142 events from 16 sports and disciplines. Category:1960s in Thailand Category:1966 in sports Category:Sport in Bangkok Category:Asian Games by year Category:1966 in Asia
title: 1966 Asian Games
